title: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
headline: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
subtitle: Floral Güffy Pool Sliders
content:
Your gift of the Floral Güffy Pool Sliders for completing “Last Dose 1 – This is an Intervention” will be added to your wardrobe before April 7.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon.
